description: Insure Academy provides advice about common planning problems, such as planning for college and preparing for retirement. This app offers advice for a growing list of important life events. It also answers over 20,000 questions about the basics of life insurance and individual fixed and variable annuities.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask insure academy how can I save for college
name: Insure.Academy
shortDescription: Answers a wide range of questions about life insurance and annuities and offers advice for life events that require these products
